time world champion. This is Greg's brother
Russ on a bomb. And he paid. [laughter] And

00:54:24.630 --> 00:54:30.520
I would point out, you know, these guys are
surfing over the hull of the Jalisco. So that

00:54:30.520 --> 00:54:39.340
ship provides a hazard kind of unlike most
other surf spots I've ever seen anywhere.

